 splits <-
   gold_mean %>% 
   time_series_split(
     assess = "1 year",
     cumulative = TRUE
     )

cv <- 
  gold_mean %>% 
  time_series_cv(
    assess      = 12 * 0.5,
    initial     = 12 * 4,
    skip        = 12 * 1,
    slice_limit = 6,
    culmulatime = FALSE
  )
splits %>% 
  tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% 
  plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 1, .interactive = FALSE)

cv %>% 
  tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% 
  plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 2, .interactive = FALSE)

Modelos

prothet_mod <- 
  prophet_reg(
    prior_scale_seasonality = 10
  ) %>% 
  set_engine("prophet") %>% 
  fit(media ~ mes, training(splits))
prothet_boost <- 
  prophet_boost() %>% 
  set_engine("prophet_xgboost") %>% 
  fit(media ~ mes + as.numeric(mes) + factor(month(mes, label = TRUE), ordered = F),
        data = training(splits))

Comparando os modelos

model_table <- 
modeltime_table(
  prothet_mod,
  prothet_boost
  )

Calibrando

calib_table <- 
  model_table %>% 
  modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits))

Test set visualization

calib_table %>% 
  modeltime_forecast(
    new_data = testing(splits),
    actual_data = gold_mean
  ) %>% 
  plot_modeltime_forecast()

Validação Cruzada

resamples_fitted <- model_table %>%
    modeltime_fit_resamples(
        resamples = cv,
        control   = control_resamples(verbose = FALSE)
    )

Forecast future

future_forecast_tbl <- 
  calib_table %>% 
  modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% 
  modeltime_forecast(
    h  = "1 year",
    actual_data = gold_mean
  )
future_forecast_tbl %>% 
  plot_modeltime_forecast()
